commitResults.messageBody:
Current findmod command does not support prefixes for targeted search.

Add "m/", "n/", "i/" prefixes for module code, module name and module instructors' names respectively.

Prefixes are optional but at least one must be present.
AB3 reads the search between different prefixes as a "And" search.
Duplicate prefixes are not allowed.
Parameters must not be empty strings.
Module/Code prefix does not allow multiple search.
Name and instructor prefix allows the use of multiple search.
Module and name prefix allows for partial keyword searches.
Instructor prefix does not allow for partial keyword searches.
